---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import MinimalFooter from '../components/MinimalFooter.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — China AI Digest"
  description="China AI Digest is an independent publication tracking China's artificial intelligence industry — policy, research, and the companies driving it."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-wrapper">
      <div class="about-header">
        <h1 class="about-title">About China AI Digest</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="about-content prose">
        <p>
          China AI Digest is an independent publication dedicated to tracking China's
          artificial intelligence industry. We cover the policies, research breakthroughs,
          and companies that are defining one of the most consequential technological
          transformations of our era.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our goal is simple: to cut through the noise and give readers a clear, accurate,
          and timely picture of what is actually happening in China's AI ecosystem —
          from government directives to lab results to startup funding rounds.
        </p>
        <h2>What We Cover</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Policy</strong> — Regulations, national strategies, and government initiatives shaping China's AI direction</li>
          <li><strong>Research</strong> — Breakthroughs from Chinese universities and labs, model releases, and technical benchmarks</li>
          <li><strong>Companies</strong> — Startups, tech giants, and the investors backing them</li>
          <li><strong>Technology</strong> — Infrastructure, chips, data, and the systems driving AI at scale</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in depth over speed and accuracy over volume. China's AI story
          is too important — and too frequently misunderstood — to be covered in
          headlines alone. Every piece we publish is written to inform, not to alarm,
          and grounded in primary sources wherever possible.
        </p>
        <h2>How We Work</h2>
        <p>
          Most of what matters in China's AI industry is published first in Chinese —
          in technical papers, regulatory filings, company announcements, and industry
          forums that rarely reach English-language audiences in their original form.
          China AI Digest exists to bridge that gap.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our editorial process starts with sourcing from Chinese-language primary
          materials: official government publications, peer-reviewed research, filings
          from Chinese regulators, and reporting from established Chinese technology
          media. We translate and synthesize these sources with care, preserving
          technical accuracy and contextual nuance rather than optimizing for speed.
        </p>
        <p>
          Where we use automated translation tools, trained editorial review follows.
          Factual claims are checked against original sources. Numbers, dates, and
          proper nouns — especially the names of companies, institutions, and
          officials — are verified before publication. We correct errors promptly
          when they are brought to our attention.
        </p>
        <h2>What To Expect</h2>
        <p>
          China AI Digest publishes new articles as significant developments warrant.
          We do not publish on a rigid schedule; we publish when we have something
          worth reading. Most weeks that means several pieces. Coverage tends to
          cluster around major policy announcements, significant model releases,
          funding events, and moments when Chinese AI development intersects
          meaningfully with global technology trends.
        </p>
        <p>
          The best way to keep up is to subscribe to our RSS feed or sign up for
          our email digest. Both are free.
        </p>
        <h2 id="contact">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          We welcome tips, corrections, pitches, and conversation. Reach us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@chinaaidigest.com">hello@chinaaidigest.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <MinimalFooter slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-wrapper {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .about-wrapper {
      padding: 40px 0 60px;
    }
  }
</style>
